high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the small round table
Pick up the remote from the table
Turn around and  walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Pick up the remote then turn off the floor lamp

high_descs: Turn around and step to the left and face the side table.
Pick up the remote from the side table.
Turn around completely and walk across the room then make a right. Then turn left to face the lamp.
Use the remote to turn off the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn off a lamp with a remote.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the small table in front of you containing the remote control.
Pick up the remote control from the table.
Turn around, walk forward across the room to the dining table, then turn right and walk forward to the wall, turn right again and walk to the tall lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote control by the dim natural light of a living room.
